section.para:
The input workflow description for Pegasus is called the DAX. It can
    be generated by running the generate_dax.sh script
    from the split directory, like this:

section.programlisting:
$ more tc.txt
tr wc {
    site condorpool {
        pfn "/usr/bin/wc"
        arch "x86_64"
        os "linux"
        type "INSTALLED"
    }
}
...
